imageshow - little 4-image WPF image renderer
by Jimmy Schementi

Ruby Usage:

  uris = %W(
    http://www.palagems.com/Images/ruby_thai_1pt21cts.jpg
  )
  require 'imageshow'
  ImageShow.new(uris)

Command Line Usage:

  > ir imageshow.rb http://www.palagems.com/Images/ruby_thai_1pt21cts.jpg

Both ways can accept either 1, 2, or 4 URIs. 

